---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Privacy Policy | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Privacy Policy" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[720px] px-6 pb-10 pt-12 text-[rgb(var(--gray-dark))]">
			<h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<section class="space-y-6">
				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">1. General Information</h2>
					<p class="m-0">
						The protection of your personal data is important to me. This website is operated as a personal blog. I
						process personal data only to the extent necessary to provide a functional website and its content.
					</p>
					<p class="m-0">This privacy policy explains what data is collected when you visit this website and how it is used.</p>
					<p class="m-0">
						Controller responsible for data processing:
						<br />
						Timo Strotmann<br />
						Horbach 27A<br />
						96193 Wachenroth<br />
						Germany<br />
						Email:
						<a class="ml-1 text-[rgb(var(--accent))] no-underline hover:underline" href="mailto:contact@strotmann.me">
							contact@strotmann.me
						</a>
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">2. Data Collection When Visiting the Website</h2>
					<p class="m-0">When you visit this website, certain data is automatically collected by the hosting provider and stored in so called server log files. This data may include:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-5">
						<li>IP address</li>
						<li>Date and time of the request</li>
						<li>Requested page or file</li>
						<li>Browser type and version</li>
						<li>Operating system</li>
						<li>Referrer URL</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="m-0">This data is technically necessary to ensure the stability, security, and proper delivery of the website. It is not used to identify you personally.</p>
					<p class="m-0">The legal basis for this processing is Article 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest).</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">3. Hosting</h2>
					<p class="m-0">This website is hosted by an external hosting provider. Personal data collected on this website is stored on the servers of the hosting provider.</p>
					<p class="m-0">The hosting provider processes the data only to the extent necessary to fulfill its service obligations and in accordance with applicable data protection laws.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">4. Cookies</h2>
					<p class="m-0">This website does not use cookies for tracking, analytics, or advertising purposes.</p>
					<p class="m-0">If technically required cookies are used by the hosting provider, this is done on the basis of Article 6(1)(f) GDPR.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">5. Umami Analytics</h2>
					<p class="m-0">This website uses Umami for anonymous website analytics.</p>
					<p class="m-0">Umami does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information. The data is used to understand traffic and improve the website.</p>
					<p class="m-0">The legal basis for this processing is Article 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest).</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">6. Embedded Content and External Resources</h2>
					<p class="m-0">This website may use external resources such as fonts, icons, or other assets that are required for proper presentation. When such resources are loaded, your IP address may be transmitted to the respective provider.</p>
					<p class="m-0">These resources are used in the interest of a consistent and user friendly presentation of the website (Article 6(1)(f) GDPR).</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">7. Contact via Email</h2>
					<p class="m-0">If you contact me via email, your message and the personal data you provide will be stored solely for the purpose of processing your request.</p>
					<p class="m-0">The legal basis for this processing is Article 6(1)(b) GDPR (processing necessary to respond to inquiries).</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">8. Your Rights</h2>
					<p class="m-0">You have the right to:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-5">
						<li>Request information about your stored personal data</li>
						<li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
						<li>Request restriction of processing</li>
						<li>Object to the processing of your data</li>
						<li>Request data portability</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="m-0">If you believe that your data is being processed unlawfully, you have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">9. Data Security</h2>
					<p class="m-0">I take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against loss, misuse, or unauthorized access.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">10. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
					<p class="m-0">I reserve the right to update this privacy policy if necessary to comply with legal requirements or to reflect changes to this website.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
